headline: RTX to release fourth quarter results on January 28, 2025
summary: RTX (NYSE: RTX) will issue its fourth quarter and full year 2024 earnings results on Tuesday, January 28, prior to the stock market opening. A conference call will take place at 8:30 a.m. ET to discuss the results and the Company's outlook for 2025.
